snippet.title: The Precinct - Official Release Date Trailer | Future Games Show 2024
snippet.description:
Check out a new look at The Precinct.

Clean up the city, uncover the truth, and embark on thrilling vehicle chases through destructible environments in this neon-noir action sandbox police game.

The Precinct is coming to PlayStation, Xbox, and PC on August 15th, 2024.

#IGN #Gaming
